channel.title: Players cant log back in? help please
channel.description:
Everytime a character logs out in my server, its filled with null, and it shows that that is a player, even though it isnt. Could anyone help me with that glitch? Also, sometimes they cant log back in, which is a major problem.
Also, if you want to check it out on my server to see it,
ip: pksc4p3.no-ip.org ip2: firesc4p3.no-ip.biz port: 5555
so go to file, new port, enter 5555 and hit ok for the noobies.
